snippet.title: Dice - The Dice Game! (bootleg of Dice Dice Dice (c)1991? IREM) (raw MAME gameplay, newly emulated)
snippet.description: Another new one that will be supported in MAME 0.241 is 'Dice - The Dice Game!' which you might think is some kind of gambling game, but is in reality a puzzle game where you have to push the dice around so that a row / column adds up to 7.  The original IREM "Dice Dice Dice" is not supported, but Jonas Jago dumped a bootleg board found in Germany some 20 years ago.
